        <div id="takedownstyle">
            <h3 id="takedown">I want to have my game removed from gamePLUS.</h3>
            <p id="takedownline">ninePLUS does not usually accept takedown requests for gamePLUS entries.</p>
            <p>This is because the only intellectual property used on gamePLUS is the game's title and a 128x128 icon.<br>This is the minimal information required to provide game displays for Quarky, as <a href="#what-is">described above</a>.</p>
            <p>If you still insist on a game's removal we may be able to remove it in exceptional cases.<br>Please use the <a href="https://www.nineplus.sh/support.html">ninePLUS contact form</a>.</p>
